Introduction

VVUP (비비업) is a four-member girl group under EgoENT. They released a pre-debut single called Doom Doom Chit on March 13, 2024. They debuted on April 1, 2024, with the single album "Locked On".

In the name 'VVUP,' 'VV' stands for 'W,' the first letter of 'WIN.' It also conveys the idea of continually ascending to the top and their intention to spread hope to the public with their unique positive energy.

In the fandom name “The Vs from ‘VVUP’ and ‘VVinie’ come together and form a W in win. We are always together anytime, anywhere.”

On August 29, EgoENT announced Hyunny's departure. Despite her efforts to recover, she decided to leave due to health problems, she has decided to focus on her personal well-being.

On December 27, EgoENT posted a photo on VVUP's SNS accounts for their upcoming comeback titled "4 Life". It was announced as a special digital single set to be released on December 30. Later on the same day Naver released articles mentioning the new member as Jiyoon.
